TODD KERPELMAN: That is true.

00:08:22.870 --> 00:08:25.480
Reinventing college,
inspired by Google

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:27.165
Games Chat number six.

00:08:27.165 --> 00:08:28.010
JOHN MCCUTCHAN: It's true.

00:08:28.010 --> 00:08:29.800
It's absolutely true.

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:32.179
TODD KERPELMAN: I think so.

00:08:32.179 --> 00:08:34.330
Do we have the cool graphic
intro yet for our

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.580
